sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant U as User
    participant R as RoomScreen
    participant AS as AppState
    participant CS as ChatSession
    participant SG as Signaling
    participant P as Peer

    U->>R: Chọn peer
    R->>AS: connectToPeer()
    AS->>CS: start()
    CS->>CS: derive key, bật relay mode
    CS->>SG: thử P2P
    U->>R: Gửi tin (sendMessage)
    R->>AS: sendMessage()
    AS->>CS: encrypt
    CS->>SG: e2e-message
    SG->>P: forward ciphertext
    P->>P: decrypt
